name: Compact Cassette (Tape) TDK A|90 (Smart Animate)
description:
Immerse yourself in the animation of a realistic TDK A|90 retro compact cassette.

Looking at this, you will be nostalgic for the warm sound of magnetic tape, remembering the wonderful evenings of wonderful music and pleasant companies.

Attention, this is very sticky.


--

Yury Zeliankouski

UX/UI Designer
